text: Mora IK is an ice hockey club in the town of Mora in Sweden. The club was established in 1935. The club lost the Swedish national championship final of 1950 wih 2-7 to Djurg√•rdens IF. The club played several seasons the old Swedish top division, Divison 1 between the mid-1940s and the mid-1970s.
